name: Nyai Part2 #6
description:
Midnight the birds reap lonely.
It's a good night, it smells good, along with the eyes that are getting softer... nyai.

When two signals are as foreign, as vibrating as they demand to meet, they become an increasingly unstoppable vortex and rhythm. Your beauty is so messy. Because of the cursed mandate of my parents, I will not take a step back...!
Guide the innocence of this soul that is still empty, this turmoil is growing... nyai. Let the scars of revenge and hate unravel somewhere...

Is there a way to describe it. Besides we enjoy the rain, let the body get wet by the rain. Teach me what love is nyai....
